OL,5, The police have failed to "bring in    
OL,6, enough talent from black communities   
OL,7, and ensure they thrive," the lead for  
OL,8, tackling racism within UK forces says. 
OL,10,FSir David Thompson, chief constable of 
OL,11,FWest Midlands Police, told BBC         
OL,12,FNewsnight racist incidents involving   
OL,13,Fofficers had been damaging.            
OL,15,FHe added it was a shame the police were
OL,16,Fnot "an employer of choice for many    
OL,17,Fcommunities".                          
